### Valid provisioning request
POST http://localhost:5000/provision
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "device_id": "device-001",
  "device_type": "cyd-esp32",
  "mac_address": "AA:BB:CC:DD:EE:FF",
  "request_type": "mqtt_config"
}

